{
    "text": "Discover Icelandic Summers through these ten video.  \"Icelandic Summer Collection \u2600\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf8\u2728  \u2022 Icelandic summers are truly amazing, here are 10 videos I\u2019ve taken that showcase some of my favorite moments. 24 hour daylight, vibrant colors, magical hikes and endless adventures. Tag someone you want to experience this with! \ud83d\udc65 \u2022 Swipe for more videos! Which one is your favorite? \ud83c\udfa5 \u2022 Song in 3rd video: \u201cMarch of Midnight\u201d by Scott Buckley Song in 5th video: \u201cWorld of Magic\u201d by Scott Buckley Song in 6th video: \u201cLife Is\u201d by Scott Buckley Song in 8th video: \u201cThe Distant Sun\u201d by Scott Buckley Song in 9th video: \u201cThe Vision\u201d by Scott Buckley Song in 10th video: \u201cDiscovery\u201d by Scott Buckley\"  #discovericeland\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf8 with @h0rdur  #iceland #summer #summervibes",
